      "description": "From grounding document: only ~5% of compounds produce meaningful SL (ΔS′ ≤ −2) in RB1-mutant cells, while 14% show genotype-independent cytotoxicity. This 1:3 ratio of SL to cytotoxic responses reflects the rarity of true network fragility points versus broad cellular stress.",
